headline: UNIVERSAL HEALTH SERVICES, INC. ANNOUNCES DATE FOR FIRST QUARTER 2025 EARNINGS RELEASE AND CONFERENCE CALL
summary: Universal Health Services, Inc. (NYSE: UHS) announced today that it will report results for its first quarter ended March 31, 2025, after the market closes on Monday, April 28, 2025. There will be a conference call for investors and analysts at 9:00 a.m. Eastern time on Tuesday, April 29, 2025
